<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Inventory Manager</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 min-h-screen">
    <nav class="bg-indigo-600 text-white shadow-lg">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-16">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <i class="fas fa-boxes text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ml-4 text-xl font-bold">Inventory Manager</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex">
                    <a href="/" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium hover:bg-indigo-500">Home</a>
                    <a href="/about" class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md text-sm font-medium bg-indigo-700">About</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white shadow overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
            <div class="px-4 py-5 sm:px-6 bg-indigo-50">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-indigo-800">About Inventory Manager</h1>
                <p class="mt-1 max-w-2xl text-sm text-gray-500">Learn more about this application and how to use it</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-200 px-4 py-5 sm:px-6">
                <div class="prose max-w-none">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">What is Inventory Manager?</h2>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        Inventory Manager is a simple but powerful web application designed to help you keep track of your items by category.
                        It allows you to organize inventory by creating item types and then adding specific items to each type with details like price and quantity.
                    </p>

                    <div class="my-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                        <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm bg-blue-50">
                            <div class="text-blue-600 text-4xl mb-3 flex justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-center mb-2">Organize by Categories</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Create custom item types to categorize your inventory the way that makes sense for your needs.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm bg-green-50">
                            <div class="text-green-600 text-4xl mb-3 flex justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-box"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-center mb-2">Track Items</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Add, edit, and delete items within each category. Monitor prices and quantities with ease.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 shadow-sm bg-purple-50">
                            <div class="text-purple-600 text-4xl mb-3 flex justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-center mb-2">Manage Inventory</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Keep track of inventory levels by adding new stock or recording used items.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">How to Use</h2>
                    
                    <div class="mb-6 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 pl-4 py-2">
                        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg text-indigo-600">Creating Item Types</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Start by creating item types on the home page. These could be categories like "Office Supplies," "Kitchen Items," or "Electronics."</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="mb-6 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 pl-4 py-2">
                        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg text-indigo-600">Adding Items</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">Click on any item type to view its dashboard. From there, you can add specific items with details like name, price per item, and quantity.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="mb-6 border-l-4 border-indigo-500 pl-4 py-2">
                        <h3 class="font-medium text-lg text-indigo-600">Managing Inventory</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">When you use items or add more stock, simply edit the item entry. The system will calculate the new quantity based on what was used and what was added.</p>
                    </div>

                    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-4">Technical Details</h2>
                    <p>This application is built with:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4 space-y-2">
                        <li><span class="font-medium">Node.js and Express</span> - Backend server and routing</li>
                        <li><span class="font-medium">MongoDB</span> - Database for storing item types and items</li>
                        <li><span class="font-medium">EJS</span> - Templating engine for rendering views</li>
                        <li><span class="font-medium">Tailwind CSS</span> - Styling and responsive design</li>
                    </ul>

                    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 p-4 mt-8">
                        <div class="flex">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-yellow-400"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-3">
                                <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-yellow-800">Tip</h3>
                                <div class="text-sm text-yellow-700">
                                    <p>For the best experience, regularly back up your data and keep your inventory updated as items are used or new stock arrives.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white mt-12">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-6 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
                <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
                    <p class="text-sm">&copy; 2025 Inventory Manager. All rights reserved.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex space-x-6">
                    <a href="/" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white">
                        <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                        <span class="ml-1">Home</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/about" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white">
                        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                        <span class="ml-1">About</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>